| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1794 — Recovery Inhibition (darkvault)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e3ecb6db-9648-5cb6-977b-a98dfe0395ad"
